            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header ">
                  <h4 class="body-card">Get the big picture</h4>
                  <p class="col-md-8"> How much profit are you making? Are your assets growing faster than your liabilities? Is cash flowing, or getting stuck?</p>

              </div>
              <div class="card-body ">

                  <div class="row body-card picture">
                      <div class="icon icon-info col-md-1 iconstyle">
                          <i class="now-ui-icons business_chart-bar-32"></i>

                      </div>

                      <div class="col-md-9">
                          <h5><a asp-action="Index" asp-controller="ProfitandLoss">Profit & Loss (Income Statement)</a></h5>
                          <p class="col-md-12">Summary of your balance expenses that datermine the profit you made</p>

                      </div>

                  </div>
                  <div class="row body-card picture">
                      <div class="icon icon-info col-md-1 iconstyle">
                          <i class="now-ui-icons shopping_tag-content"></i>
                      </div>

                      <div class="col-md-9">
                          <h5><a asp-action="Index" asp-controller="ReportAccountTransaction">Transactions</a></h5>
                          <p class="col-md-12">Summary of your balance expenses that datermine the profit you made</p>

                      </div>

                  </div>
                  <div class="row body-card picture">
                      <div class="icon icon-info col-md-1 iconstyle">
                          <i class="now-ui-icons education_paper"></i>
                      </div>

                      <div class="col-md-9">
                          <h5><a asp-action="Index" asp-controller="BalanceSheet">Balance Sheet</a></h5>
                          <p class="col-md-12">
                              Snapshot of what your business owns or
                              is due to receive from other (assets), whats its own to others
                              (liabilities) and what you've invested ar retained in your company (Equity)
                          </p>

                      </div>

                  </div>

                  <div class="row body-card picture">
                      <div class="icon icon-info col-md-1 iconstyle">
                          <i class="now-ui-icons business_money-coins"></i>
                      </div>

                      <div class="col-md-9">
                          <h5><a asp-action="Index" asp-controller="AccountCashFlow">Cash Flow</a></h5>
                          <p class="col-md-12">
                              Cashing coming in and going out of your business.
                              Includes items not included in the profit and loss such as repayment
                              of loan principal and owner drawings (paying yourself)
                          </p>

                      </div>

                  </div>
              </div>

          </div>
      </div>
